data.description: Welcome to 557 Shadow Glenn Place!!This gorgeous 1152 sq ft two-story two bedroom, one and one-half bathroom town home is up for rent beginning February 1st/15! Spacious rooms and lots of great upgrades makes this the perfect home for you! There are new appliances in the large bright kitchen as well as a washer and dryer in the unit! Huge master bedroom with a HUMONGOUS closet is capable of storing anything!! New laminate wood floors upstairs, new paint, new lights, fans, etc...!! Step out onto the private screened patio and enjoy your own peaceful retreat! Two parking spaces right in front of the residence. Great town home community! The area is safe, well taken care of, great schools nearby, etc!! Also, there is a community pool as well! Close to malls, grocery stores, fitness centers, etc! This town home can be yours to enjoy and love! Now accepting applications- please reply to this email or call 321-209-1232 asap to get an application!! Floor Plan/Unit Amenities: * All Appliances (Fridge, Stove & Dishwasher) * Washer/Dryer in unit!!* Garbage Disposal * Large Closets*Huge storage area under the stairs * Air Conditioning * Patio/Balcony Property Amenities: * Extra Storage*Close to grocery stores*Close to Malls * Close to Fitness Center * Public Transportation Lease Terms:12 Months Parking:Type -2 spots @ Surface LotPet Policy:Cats and Dogs are allowed. Breed restrictions apply as well as number of pets. Call Today! 321-209-1232Tenant responsible for all utilities monthly.
